 出现多处异常，部分错误可关联到 Ad 和 Redis 服务。\n\n接下来我将基于拓扑和根因定位技术进一步分析这些调用链。下一阶段将检查因果关系和传播路径。", "log_analysis_findings": "日志数据已成功加载。以下是从UUID和指定时间范围内提取的错误日志概况：\n\n### 关键日志提取\n\n#### 1. 错误类型和常见问题\n- **context deadline exceeded**: 多次被记录，主要来自 `frontend` 服务，报错内容涉及 `failed to get ads`，提示与 `adservice` 服务的交互出现超时问题。\n- **stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL**: 发生在 `frontend` 服务中，表示连接在传输中被取消。\n\n#### 2. 异常组件和故障原因\n- **Component**: adservice\n  - **Reason**: 由于频繁出现的超时错误（`context deadline exceeded`），怀疑是 `adservice` 服务处理请求的延迟或负载过高，导致 `frontend` 无法成功获取广告。\n  - **Evidence**: \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n\n- **Java Exception**: 在 `adservice` 服务中发现 Java 异常，`java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`，可能与触发条件或配置文件导致的问题有关。\n  - **Evidence**: \"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n\n### 关键词列表\n- detected_log_keys: [\"context deadline exceeded\", \"stream terminated by RST_STREAM\", \"DeadlineExceeded\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Byteman\", \"java.lang.Exception\"]\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"context deadline exceeded\",\n    \"stream terminated by RST_STREAM\",\n    \"DeadlineExceeded\",\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Byteman\",\n    \"java.lang.Exception\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"频繁超时，可能是服务负载过高或响应速度慢导致'session can't be completed in time'.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Java 异常可能与未正确配置的 Byteman agent 或多次加载相关。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现指向 `adservice` 的响应延迟为主要故障根因，可能与服务配置问题相关，如 Byteman agent 的异常加载。需要进一步就 adservice 的负载和配置进行深度分析和优化。", "metric_analysis_findings": "已经成功加载指标数据。以下是故障期间显著的异常指标变化：\n\n### 异常指标数据\n```csv\nmetric_type,service_name,pod_name,node_name,metric_name,normal_median,fault_median,normal_p99,fault_p99,median_change_ratio,p99_change_ratio\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-0,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,2.78,0.0,2.0\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-0,N/A,client_error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.0,2.78,0.0,2.0\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-1,N/A,rrt,1441.17,1490.0,2057.0,57926.2,0.0333,1.8628\nservice,paymentservice,paymentservice-1,N/A,rrt_max,1689.5,1745.0,3098.97,58098.4,0.0323,1.7974\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-2,N/A,rrt_max,3037.0,2696.0,8296.73,75907.2,0.119,1.6059\nservice,emailservice,emailservice-2,N/A,rrt_max,3257.0,3195.0,6153.04,50799.4,0.0192,1.5678\nservice,currencyservice,currencyservice-0,N/A,rrt_max,3486.5,3868.0,8622.16,65930.6,0.1037,1.5374\nservice,cartservice,cartservice-2,N/A,rrt,1321.55,1253.67,1641.52,9250.86,0.0527,1.3972\nservice,adservice,adservice-0,N/A,client_error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.76,3.39,0.0,1.2672\nservice,adservice,adservice-0,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.76,3.39,0.0,1.2672\nservice,frontend,frontend-0,N/A,rrt,11868.34,38698.82,13533.0,51597.24,1.0612,1.1689\nservice,frontend,frontend-1,N/A,rrt,12134.22,36140.78,13380.43,46011.54,0.9946,1.0988\nservice,frontend,frontend-2,N/A,rrt,12175.62,36015.48,13102.33,44465.4,0.9894,1.0896\nservice,frontend,frontend-0,N/A,rrt_max,195508.0,603788.0,286504.62,650053.8,1.0216,0.7764\nservice,frontend,frontend-2,N/A,rrt_max,234163.5,611115.0,299166.95,676867.0,0.8919,0.7739\nservice,frontend,frontend-1,N/A,rrt_max,242468.0,609758.0,286020.04,670886.8,0.862,0.8044\nservice,emailservice,emailservice-2,N/A,rrt,1727.61,1756.67,2384.62,5836.3,0.0167,0.8397\nservice,shippingservice,shippingservice-1,N/A,rrt_max,1531.5,1568.0,3483.62,8094.0,0.0236,0.7964\ntidb,tidb-tikv,N/A,N/A,io_util,0.0,0.0,0.48,0.23,0.0,0.7131\nservice,shippingservice,shippingservice-2,N/A,rrt_max,1663.0,1544.0,